Depends: libopenzwave1.0, python, ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}
Description: py-openzwave is a python wrapper around the open-zwave project.
 The wrapper allows you to control a z-wave network from python.
 This wrapper is still a work in progress, but the basic skeleton is
 in place (network scanning, and turning a device on or off).
